Template: tg-torrent-bot/telegram_token
Type: string
Description: 1/4. Enter telegram bot token
 Open @BotFather bot in Telegram and get a token for the bot.

Template: tg-torrent-bot/rutracker_username
Type: string
Description: 2/4. Enter username for rutracker.org
 Bot needs to be signed in to rutracker.org to be able to search for torrents.
 You can use your account if you already have it, or you can create a new one.

Template: tg-torrent-bot/rutracker_password
Type: string
Description: 3/4. Enter password for rutracker.org

Template: tg-torrent-bot/torrents_dir
Type: string
Description: 4/4. Enter path to .torrent files directory
 Here the bot will put .torrent files when user clicks download-link.
 You can set up your torrent-daemon to listen to this directory.